<view class="container"><view class="notice"><text class="notice-dot"></text><text>仅和同校同学交易，请注意保护隐私。</text></view><scroll-view scroll-y class="msg-list" scroll-into-view="{{scrollToView}}" scroll-with-animation bindscrolltoupper="loadMore" upper-threshold="50"><view wx:if="{{loadingMore}}" class="loading-more">正在加载更早的消息</view><view wx:if="{{messages.length === 0 && !loadingMore}}" class="chat-empty"><text>从一句“你好”开始吧</text></view><block wx:for="{{messages}}" wx:key="_id"><view class="msg-item {{item.senderOpenid === myOpenid ? 'mine' : 'other'}}" id="msg-{{item._id}}"><text class="msg-content">{{item.content}}</text><text class="msg-time">{{item.createTimeFormat}}</text></view></block></scroll-view><view class="input-bar"><input placeholder="说点什么…" value="{{inputText}}" bindinput="onInput" bindconfirm="sendMsg" confirm-type="send"/><view class="wechat-action pressable" bindtap="sendMyWechat">微信号</view></view></view>
